text: The Senior Women's T20 League is a women's Twenty20 competition in India. 37 domestic team compete in the tournament. The inaugural tournament was conducted in season 2008/09 and since then has been conducted every year. 2019–20 Senior Women's T20 League was the twelfth edition of the tournament. Railways are the current champion.
